> #onleave:hook > on_leave
--------------------
 ! when a player leaves the game.
  @ tick
--------------------
 -> UUID: UUID
 ~~{ pdata }~~
 -> index: int
--------------------
 ...
--------------------
 - <UUID> is the UUID of the player that left.
 
 - if 'pdata' is installed:
    - <index> contains the pdata-index of the player that left.

 - for general use.
--------------------